Plain Aligner is a very plain bilingual text aligner that transforms plain text files with the same number of lines into a TMX.

It has no external dependencies besides click.

Pytest is required to run the tests.

Usage: palign [OPTIONS] DEST
  All options are required

Options:
  languages should be ISO language codes e.g. es-ES

  -tf, --tar-file PATH TO SOURCE FILE
  -sf, --src-file PATH TO TARGET FILE
  -tl, --tar-lang
  -sl, --src-lang
  --help

  DEST is the path to the TMX


